--- SETTING UP THE VM ---

1. Downloaded the latest version of virtualbox for Ubuntu as a debian package and installed it.

2. A virtual machine was created, with a vdi-image as hard-disk. Dynamic partition was used with a maximum size of 30 GB.

3. Downloaded Lubuntu 14.10 ISO image, and installed it in the virtual machine.

4. Inside the virtual machine lubuntu os, the package 'virtualbox-guest-dkms' to correct the screen size.


